{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"78cd87a4-b49b-485c-a321-21cc2b799ee6","content":"The directory is empty, so I'll give you the recommended setup directly.\n\n## 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\nWith **MSTest.Sdk**, the project file is minimal:\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` brings in the test framework, runner, and analyzers automatically. No extra `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n## 2. Enable parallel execution (`.runsettings`)\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file at the project root:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>           <!-- 0 = use all logical processors -->\n      <Scope>MethodLevel</Scope>     <!-- parallelize across methods (or ClassLevel) -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nThen reference it in your csproj (inside `<PropertyGroup>`):\n\n```xml\n<RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n```\n\n## 3. Run database tests sequentially\n\nUse the `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute on a test class:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanInsertRecord() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanQueryRecords() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- `[DoNotParallelize]` on a class pulls **all its methods** out of the parallel pool — they run sequentially and never concurrently with each other.\n- Everything else runs in parallel per your `.runsettings`.\n- `Workers=0` auto-scales to your CPU count; set a fixed number if you prefer.\n- `Scope=MethodLevel` gives maximum parallelism; use `ClassLevel` if tests within a class share state.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fabddc61-3afa-4c7c-8b76-d8cbba1f8fa6","outputTokens":554,"requestId":"604F:2EF340:263C247:28D9E48:6A031282"},"id":"57c4a369-dcc1-4613-b9e6-a6a1b25ffe49","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:44:15.009Z","parentId":"93f80cbd-535a-4480-aabe-066c3fc6b106"}
